<br>
I get about half a blue bubble for every blue con there besides the shrooms i pick some zalniaks and lightcrawlers for variation and this make me gain xp rather quick (enough to hunt there)<br>
<br>
If you can get C3 and Aego (rather often casted in the nexus) this zone really rocks <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  With a damage shield, 1800HP and awesome mana regen. just hit red ones and keep chain casting (got 3 yellow bubbles in about 1 hour). some would call that cheating but then again i usualy die from C3 because i think i can win from every mob with it... and err.. i can't.<br>
<br>
